file_content.text: We got as many taps as we could into the system. Anything?
I installed your devices. Tell me where the worm is, and this will be over.
This system's got more bugs than a Geonosian nursery. Give me a lock on our target.
Getting a fix on his location... got it. Go.
I'm tracing. Put in another tap.
No luck yet. We need a jackpoint. Put in a tap.
You're not supposed to be here.
